- Add tekken report [amleczko]

-------------------

- Update quality CR in project wizard [amleczko]

-------------------

- Add more details to customer report [amleczko]


2.1.42 (2016-02-02)
-------------------

- Update contract listing view [amleczko]


2.1.41 (2016-02-02)
-------------------

- Add contract listing [amleczko]


2.1.40 (2015-02-18)
-------------------

- increase idnormalizer limit to allow longer project names [amleczko]


2.1.39 (2015-02-11)
-------------------

- add open by customer field to quality reports [amleczko]
- refactor quality reports and remove pivoat tables [amleczko]


2.1.38 (2015-01-28)
-------------------

- fix quality reports to handle unicode properly [amleczko]


2.1.37 (2015-01-24)
-------------------

- add contract to all time entries groupby [amleczko]


2.1.36 (2014-10-06)
-------------------

- update quality reports [amleczko]


2.1.35 (2014-08-04)
-------------------

- fix UI / permissions for customer [amleczko]


2.1.34 (2014-07-16)
-------------------

- change logic in quality reports [amleczko]


2.1.33 (2014-07-08)
-------------------

- new report for last 1000 hours [amleczko]
- small fixes to previous reports [amleczko]


2.1.32 (2014-07-07)
-------------------

- quality report round down to 1 decimal [amleczko]


2.1.31 (2014-07-03)
-------------------

- fix add time entry modal dialog [amleczko]
- fix report index [amleczko]
- show all projects in report, not only active [amleczko]
- fix json export from reports [amleczko]


2.1.30 (2014-07-03)
-------------------

- fix project wizard form to avoid creation empty tickets [amleczko]
- new quality report: we vs. customer [amleczko]
- searchable milestones [amleczko]
- use dismax parser [amleczko]
- integrate sql search in solr [amleczko]
- fix transaction handling when working with trac [amleczko]
- make sure contract field is visible and required [amleczko]
- add filters to time entries migrate [amleczko]
- fix bug with multi schema select [amleczko]
- cleanup newrelic [amleczko]
- fix bug in fastticketing [amleczko]
- fix bug in wizard [amleczko]

2.1.20 (2014-02-05)
-------------------

- fix paths [amleczko]
- remove outstanding tickets [amleczko]
- fix icons [amleczko]
- add user stats [amleczko]
- add default form actions [amleczko]
- simplify angularjs integration [amleczko]
- fix redis pub/sub [amleczko]
- include feedly notifications [amleczko]
- add redis kanbanboard support [amleczko]
- fixes to kanbanboard [amleczko]
- performance fixes for my_time_entries report [amleczko]
- fix search after moving to new deform [amleczko]
- fixes for migrate form [amleczko]


2.1.10 (2014-01-20)
-------------------

- fix change_state problem in estimations tab [amleczko]
- fix tekken `done` column [amleczko]
- add user costs [amleczko]
- small bug fixing [amleczko]
- new fields for quality report [amleczko]
- removes deprecated function get_user_by_login [amleczko]
- upgrade to deform 0.9.9 [amleczko]
- make project related chosen field more automatic [amleczko]
- add quick link to reports from tekken [amleczko]
- add proper HTML title tag [amleczko]
- refactor notifications [amleczko]
- new quality report - operator [amleczko]
- fix problem with js select in teken listing [amleczko]
- svn_login no longer required during user creation [amleczko]
- fix author override in new time entry creation [amleczko]
- estimations popover [amleczko]
- automatization for wizard form [amleczko]
- automatization for estimation wf_state [amleczko]
- Enable newrelic hooks if config is available [amleczko]
- internal develope can create customer_request [amleczko]
- fix populate_with_dummies script [amleczko]
- update dashboard [amleczko]
- add fixes for wizard project form [amleczko]
- fix security check in tekken view [amleczko]
- update quality reports [amleczko]
- Add massive time entry move [amleczko]
- Add workflow state change form for customer request listing (tekken) [amleczko]
- fix reports filtering [amleczko]
- fix tekken js [amleczko]
- switch to mandrill API [amleczko]
- remove backlog from main menu [amleczko]
- refactoring contracts [amleczko]


2.0 (2013-09-10)
------------------

- handle sorting gracefully [amleczko]
- fix smtp port [amleczko]
- make sure xmlrpc is handling dns errors [amleczko]
- fix owner role bug [amleczko]
- fix problem with proxy in front of xml-rpc protocol [amleczko]
- hide gevent-psycopg2 for a moment [amleczko]
- switch to green psycopg2 [amleczko]
- new dashboard [amleczko]
- kanban board bug fixes [amleczko]

2.0a (2013-08-26)
-----------------

- Kanban board [amleczko]
- Switch to socket.io [amleczko]


1.2.1 (2013-08-20)
------------------

- ga tracking code slot [amleczko]


1.2 (2013-08-14)
----------------

- fix problem with formalchemy validation [amleczko]
- fix various security problems and update test coverage [amleczko]


1.1 (2013-08-13)
----------------

- merge integration with penelope.trac [amleczko]


1.0 (2013-08-12)
----------------

- merge por.dashboard, por.models and por.gdata [amleczko]
